PHLAWD is available via Homebrew.

1. Install homebrew (if you haven't already)
    ruby -e "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.github.com/Homebrew/homebrew/go/install)"

2. Tap the Homebrew/science tap
    brew tap homebrew/science

3. Download, compile, and install PHLAWD and its dependencies
    brew install phlawd
